  echo -e "
Version: 3.3
  + Added more compability for Debian based distros & UNIX/POSIX systems.
  + Detect VM and DE/WM are more dynamic.
  + \"r.txt\" file with default banner is no longer needed.
  Rofetch can now be executed in any location of your system.
  + Rewrote the whole code and made it more legible for programmers.
  + Checks for dependencies on the first execution.
  Marker file \".rofetch-first-execution\" will be created in \"/tmp/\" directory.
  - Inspiration quotes variable was commented out and will be a WIP for now
  since it's been consuming a little bit too much of user execution time.

Version: 4.0
  + New temporary and permanent changeable banner color with configuration file ($HOME/.config/rofetch-color-config)
  + New temporary and permanent changeable secondary string color with configuration file ($HOME/.config/rofetch-color-config)
  + New reset default colors flag
  + Fixed IPv4 hanging on startup
  + Improved code and comments legibility
  + Overall code cleanup and improvements
  "
  exit 0
}

